<i>adjective</i>: 푹신푹신하다 [푹씬푹씬하다], 푸근하다 [푸근하다], 폭신폭신하다 [폭씬폭씬하다], 포근하다 [포근하다], 편하다 [편하다], 편안하다 [펴난하다], 오붓하다 [오부타다], 안락하다 [알라카다], 느긋하다 [느그타다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>푹신푹신하다 [푹씬푹씬하다]</dt><br>
<dd>soft; snug; comfortable</dd><br>
<dd>매우 푸근하게 부드럽고 탄력이 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Feeling soft and elastic, in a very snug way.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>푸근하다 [푸근하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. cozy; snug; soft</dd><br>
<dd>꽤 두꺼운 물건이나 자리가 부드럽고 따뜻하다.</dd><br>
<dd>A substantially thick object or seat being soft and warm.</dd><br>
<dd>2. comfortable</dd><br>
<dd>느낌이나 분위기가 부드럽고 따뜻하여 편안하다.</dd><br>
<dd>A feeling or atmosphere that is comfortable because it is soft and warm.</dd><br>
<dd>3. warm</dd><br>
<dd>날씨가 바람이 없고 꽤 따뜻하다.</dd><br>
<dd>The weather being windless and quite warm.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>폭신폭신하다 [폭씬폭씬하다]</dt><br>
<dd>soft; snug; comfortable</dd><br>
<dd>매우 포근하게 부드럽고 탄력이 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Feeling soft and elastic, in a very snug way.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>포근하다 [포근하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. cozy; snug; soft</dd><br>
<dd>두꺼운 물건이나 자리가 보드랍고 따뜻하다.</dd><br>
<dd>A thick object or seat being soft and warm.</dd><br>
<dd>2. comfortable</dd><br>
<dd>느낌이나 분위기가 보드랍고 따뜻하여 편안하다.</dd><br>
<dd>A feeling or atmosphere that is comfortable because it is soft and warm.</dd><br>
<dd>3. warm</dd><br>
<dd>날씨가 바람이 없고 따뜻하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Weather being windless and warm.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>편하다 [편하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. comfortable; easy; peaceful</dd><br>
<dd>몸이나 마음이 괴롭지 않고 좋다.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of one's body or mind being good, neither sick, nor troubled.</dd><br>
<dd>2. handy; easy; simple; convenient</dd><br>
<dd>쉽고 간편하다.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being easy and simple.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>편안하다 [펴난하다]</dt><br>
<dd>comfortable; being at ease</dd><br>
<dd>몸이나 마음이 편하고 좋다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's body or mind being relaxed and good.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>오붓하다 [오부타다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. peaceful; comfortable</dd><br>
<dd>아늑하고 정답다.</dd><br>
<dd>Cozy and friendly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. sufficient; moderately wealthy; well</dd><br>
<dd>살림이나 수입이 넉넉하여 실속 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's household size or income being enough and substantial.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>안락하다 [알라카다]</dt><br>
<dd>comfortable; carefree</dd><br>
<dd>근심이나 걱정 없이 몸과 마음이 편안하고 즐겁다.</dd><br>
<dd>Feeling pleasant and comfortable mentally and physically without anxiety.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>느긋하다 [느그타다]</dt><br>
<dd>comfortable; relaxed; carefree</dd><br>
<dd>서두르지 않고 마음의 여유가 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Keeping one's composure and not hurrying.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>